name: HOME: HEN500K
description:
Mums hold much sentimental meaning for me. My mother planted them in the garden in every house, in every city, in every state we ever lived. A seemingly trivial detail in the grand scheme of the story of my life. But this simple mundane act became a sort of anchor for me. One aspect of my life that remained untouched - changed - tainted. A constant indicator telling where I am - Home - and everything that word means to me...

"Home" is my first photography mint on any NFT platform and celebrates not just the colors of our current fall season, but HEN500K as well!
